projects.title: Efflorescence Single
projects.description: Efflorescence is a representation of growth during a turbulent time

projects.title: Liberosis EP
projects.description: Liberosis is my first EP, released in 2024. It's a collection of 5 tracks that explore the themes of being free from your thoughts.

projects.title: End of Summer Rooftop Melodic House Mix
projects.description: A mix I made for the end of summer, released in 2023. It features my favorite melodic house tracks from artists like Odesza, Fred Again, Anyma, Julian Gray, and more. This mix is meant for chill rooftop summer parties.

projects.title: Penguin Holiday Card Maker
projects.description: Make a holiday card for your friends and family, using AI generated stickers in the style of Stardew Valley. Built with React + Konva.

projects.title: Penguin Vibe Mood Assessment
projects.description: Waddle around and express yourself with emojis in this digital sanctuary, with custom lo-fi beats I made. Based on your emojis, the website will give you a mood assessment.

projects.title: Birthday Puzzle Hunt
projects.description: Test your puzzle hunt skills in this personalized birthday puzzle hunt I made for my birthday. Good luck!
